title: 2. xXx: The Return of Xander Cage $20M
text: Action packed. By arussel04 You gotta see it. Action packed. Been waiting for a movie that will not put me asleep and it didn't. Action, action, action.... Nice movie Wasn't bad to watch for a night. Predictable yes but nevertheless I enjoyed it.... Not the best, also not too bad. By simplytj Its fun, good action, and vin diesel with some good one liners. Don't go in expecting much else. Its the kind of movie to just have fun and chill. Not for the "smart" and definitely not boring. Go... Cool action flic.,, Cant wait for the new XXX .., with all the new characters.... HEY, IT'S TRIPLE XXX ACTION FROM BEGINNING TO END! By speedygodzilla IF I WANTED TO GO SEE A GIRLIE MOVIE I WOULD HAVE GONE TO SEE "LALA LAND" WITH A BOX OF TISSUES AND THE NEVER TRUMP CROWD.
